## Template Examples

### Correct usage (reading from library first)
```html
<!-- soho-button: @Input sohoButton="primary" verified from lib/button/soho-button.component.d.ts -->
<button soho-button="primary" (click)="onSave()">Save</button>

<!-- soho-datagrid: @Inputs [columns] [dataset] verified from lib/datagrid/ -->
<soho-datagrid
  [columns]="columns"
  [dataset]="rows"
  [selectable]="'single'"
  (rowActivated)="onRowActivated($event)">
</soho-datagrid>
```

### Forbidden — DO NOT do this
```html
<!-- ❌ Never initialize IDS controls via jQuery in templates -->
<div id="my-grid"></div>
<!-- ❌ Never guess prop names — always verify in the .d.ts -->
<soho-datagrid [data]="rows">   <!-- WRONG: property is [dataset] -->
```

