## Checking Available Options Interfaces

Each component exposes a typed `Options` interface. Example lookup for `SohoDataGridOptions`:
1. Open `lib/datagrid/soho-datagrid.component.d.ts`
2. Find `set gridOptions(gridOptions: SohoDataGridOptions)` — this shows the options type
3. Check `ids-enterprise-typings` (via the `index.d.ts`) for the full `SohoDataGridOptions` interface shape

---

## Discovering New Components

If you need a component not listed above:
1. Search `scraped_components/_index.json` for the component by name.
2. Map its slug to the matching folder in `ids-enterprise-ng/lib/`.
3. Read the `.component.d.ts` and at least one `example-*_html/page.html` before generating code.
